Charlotte Blakeway was discovered dead in the bath at her home in Shropshire . 
  The 17-year-old had suffered an epileptic fit and was found dead  . 
  She was studying film, performance, English and sociology at Shrewsbury Sixth Form College . 
  Friends have paid tribute to the student who was described as bright and enthusiastic . 
  Police said her death is not being treated as suspicious . 
 